com.aylanetworks.aylasdk.localdevice

类 AylaLocalProperty<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.aylanetworks.aylasdk.AylaProperty<T>
      • com.aylanetworks.aylasdk.localdevice.AylaLocalProperty<T>
  • 类型参数:
    T - the base type, inherited from AylaProperty.

    public class AylaLocalProperty<T>
extends AylaProperty<T>
    The AylaLocalProperty class is responsible for the creation of datapoints on the LocalDevice as well as obtaining the current values from the device.

      • pushUpdateToCloud

        public void pushUpdateToCloud()
        Creates a datapoint on the cloud for this property using the current value. This is used by the LocalDevice SDK to reflect changes on the device obtained via a local connection on the cloud service.
